						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="italic">Slab built into the back-wall of Lakumēśvara temple.</hi></p>						

						<p>16th-17th Century A.D.</p>						

						<p>This record, in characters of about the <hi rend="bold">16th-17th Century A.D.,</hi> is dated in the cyclic year <hi rend="bold">Pārthiva, Kārttika, s11u. 7.</hi> The details cannot be verified.</p>						

						<p>It records a gift of <hi rend="italic">mānya</hi> to Chauṇḍarasa by <hi rend="bold">Bammanāsana Khāna-sāhēba (?).</hi></p>						

